					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>It registers the gift of taxes for burning 3 perpetual lamps to the temple of Sri Rudrasōlai Uḍaiyār at Karaikkōṭṭu Brahmadēsam in Dāmal-nāḍu in Jayaṅkoṇḍasōḷamaṇḍalam. The gift was made on the order of Pōvindarasar, the agent of the <hi rend="italic">Mahāpradhāṉi</hi> Sōmaiya Daṇṇāyaka. </p>						

						</summary>
